@29751 = ~Headknocker was crafted by the ogress Shavauntea as a "gift" for her husband, Grothak the Stupid.  Her hope was that the club could be used to "knock sense into empty head."  Shavauntea was quite surprised to find that the weapon had the opposite effect when she brought it down upon her husband's unsuspecting head.  The club was thought to have been destroyed in the battle between the two lovers after Grothak regained his senses.  Obviously, this was not the case.

