@31376 = ~Usually plate mail is reserved for those strong enough to wear it.  It did not matter that there were many fine warriors in the land who could benefit from the extra protection that plate mail could lend them.  Those unfortunate enough to be of the slender side were reserved to use nothing heavier than chain mail.  That is until a resourceful young armorsmith happened on an owl's feather enchantment that helped her to create plate mail that weighed half as much as regular plate mail.  Needless to say, that particular armorsmith became very popular with the slender warriors of the region.

