@31545 = ~The story of Silentkiller is a common tale that may, or may not, be true.  The story tells of two brothers who vied for the attention, and throne, of their ailing father.  When the elder brother was named king by his dying sire, the younger was furious and vowed to take the throne as his own.  To this end he commissioned the making of Silentkiller to aid him in his brother's murder.

