@33176 = ~This small barbarian bow is foreign to the lands of Icewind Dale, having been made by the distant warrior-priests of Vaasa.  Its history is not rich, having been used by the chief hunter of a small tribe for decades.  The bow later fell into the hands of invaders after the tribe was wiped out.  Its obvious "barbarian" look could be unappealing to stylish urban adventurers.  Made of yew and wrapped with thin furs, the bow looks rugged and practical.  The grip of the bow has a chipped and faded painting of a large eye on each side.

