@33182 = ~The famed halfling hunter Herrian Smallhill was well known for his ability to fell large numbers of rabbits in a single day.  Though Herrian repeatedly was challenged to displays of "real" hunting skill, he always returned to his home near Corm Orp to provide rabbits for his community.  A noble elven hunter named Shidan Imraith challenged the halfling to a hunting contest in 1197 DR.  When Herrian emerged at the victor, the proud elf became so enraged that he ordered his men to kill the halfling.  Though Imraith's house was disgraced for the action and Shidan was brought to justice, Herrian's fine yew bow disappeared.

