Traveling companions,

Regrettably, I could not remain until we declared our farewells and bid each other pleasant journeys.  Good Nathaniel was in a fretful hurry to warn the Ten-Towns about the peril they face at the hands of the Legion of the Chimera, so we took to the skies once able.  I did, however, have time to quickly whip together a nice beverage - I hope you can make good use of it.

