@36191 = ~I am <GABBER>!  I have come to rid this land of the Legion of the Chimera and all who follow its foul banner!~
@36358 = ~<GABBER>, from the east, you say?  Either you're a very bad liar, or you're just nervous about meeting their lordships, Isair and Madae.  Hmm...  You seem like a friendly face to me...  I really do not sense any threat in your voice...  Fine, you may enter, but you must go directly to see Xavier Torsend, our Minister of Affairs.~
@36359 = ~Is that so, *<GABBER>?!*  I have no orders for a *<GABBER>* seeking an audience with their lordships, Isair and Madae!  Even Xavier Torsend, our Minister of Affairs, would have mentioned your arrival to me so I could direct you to get a delegate pass!  No, you are obviously intruders - and as intruders, you will die where you stand!  Guards!  Attack!~
@36756 = ~My name is <GABBER>.~
@36758 = ~<GABBER>, is it?  How mortally simple.  Do you know what I am?  Do you know where I hail from?~
@36764 = ~I must say, I have never met a mortal who was so knowledgeable about the Blood War and the denizens of the Abyss.  I respect this.  In fact, I shall let you live, as a reward for your impressive knowledge.  Now, I have things I must attend to.  Farewell, <GABBER>, but know that if we meet again, I will consume you.~
@36884 = ~The Slayer Knights of Xvim are considered one of the deadliest warriors in any kingdom.  One of the things that makes them so deadly, besides being demon kin, is their skill with their specially forged greatswords; the Greatsword of the Soulless.  Being the common weapon of knights, the primary function of greatswords is cleaving mounted knights and breaking up pike formations.  However, in the efficient hands of a Slayer Knight of Xvim, this particular greatsword will cleave through the bodies of their targets, and literally suck out the target's lifeblood.  The Greatsword of the Soulless is the primary weapon of the Slayer Knights of Xvim.

